column5: Can anyone give me a good web site address for weather info for the Ear Falls and Red Lake area?
Gary,Try this web site for weather conditions in Ontario:www.ontarioweather.comRemember to keep your eyes open and your feet dry.S.v.m
Try theweathernetwork.com Dryden was the closest to Ear Falls I could find.
www.weather.com has info on red lake, www.iwon.com has weather for most of canada
http://town.earfalls.on.ca/ Here you go, I fish there every June.
